fields.description: Drone crashed while flying at the NHRA Gainesville race
fields.damage_desc: DJI Mavic 3 Pro drone was destroyed
fields.notes: After losing connection the drone began RTH by flying straight up.  The controller was in Sport Mode and obstacle avoidance was not activated.  The drone struck the overhanging soffit of the Gainesville Raceway Timing Tower and fell to the ground in an unoccupied area.
